            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "this issue is caused by nvim trying to reset the window icon when exiting. Precisely, it just hangs up while calling `SendMessage` with `WM_SETICON`. The reason this doesn't happen when using e.g. windows terminal is because nvim only tries to reset the window icon when it got an original one while starting. Conhost provides this, but Windows Terminal doesn't.",
